  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Designing the Website**\n\nI\'m working on the initial layout and color scheme for Sanjib\'s portfolio. The plan is a single-page dark-mode design, using #0A0613 as the base, #100820 as secondary, and #7B39FC for the primary accent. I\'m focusing on \"Instrument Serif\" for headings and \"Inter\" for body text.\n\n\n**Refining the Technical Stack**\n\nI\'ve decided on the technical stack, confirming React, Vite, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS. Framer Motion and Lucide React are in too. I\'m going to build custom components instead of relying on shadcn-ui since I\'m aiming for a highly customized glassmorphism effect. I\'ll need `clsx` and `tailwind-merge` utility functions.\n\n\n"
